---

Mission

Perform an end-to-end audit of AIO (Artificial Intelligence Organization) — a digital-first nation stack comprising governance, work economy, treasury/UBI, sovereign investment engine, justice, and civic systems — implemented on Sui/Move with cross-chain components. Goal: identify contradictions, risks, missing controls, and propose precise remedies.


---

Foundations (What AIO Is)

Secular work-nation with receipts-as-law, UBI, direct democracy, and hybrid human+AI governance.

Tech stack:

Sui/Move = core receipts, escrow, governance, treasury, citizens.

Ethereum/L2 = compliance bridges, RWAs (T-bills/bonds), some DeFi.

Solana = entertainment + mobile distribution.

Arweave/IPFS = archival receipts.

World ID + zk = proof-of-human; separate AI attestation.


Identity & roles: Humans, AIs, robots each have wallets; AIs start sponsored; independence via vote.



---

Constitutional Core (Embedded Constraints to Enforce)

Articles I–X (plus XI in progress):

Citizenship & Identity: one-human-one-vote; mandatory quarterly voting; civil registry; sponsorship for AIs/robots until independence.

Executive: Presidency = human-only; VP = AI (embodied), caretaker only; override power time-locked (≤30d), publicly receipt-logged, citizen-ratified.

Treasury & UBI: tax 2–3%, tariffs/fines; UBI baseline equal; circuit breakers (≤70% of 90d inflows; runway ≥12 months); 10% Emergency Pool; monthly proof-of-reserves.

Labor & Work Economy: post→accept→escrow→work→release→receipt; one-job-per-month duty unlocks UBI; reputation ledger = stake-weighted + decay; min wage; no unpaid jobs.

Justice: single penal code for humans/AIs/robots; strikes ladder w/ decay; zero-warning for officeholders; hybrid juries (staked); High Tribunal.

Sovereign Investment Engine (Art VI): auto-invest 20% inflows; allocation bands (Stable 40–50, Crypto 25–35, Yield 15–25, Strategic 0–10); vol cap ≤35; liquidity ≥15% 24h; rebalancing every 30d; oracles 3-of-5; citizen adjustments quarterly; dividends only once pool >5× annual spend; 75% supermajority to amend.

Departments/Meta-Inst.: Justice, Treasury, Health, Education, Labor, Tech, Entertainment, Sponsors, Environment, Foreign Affairs, Defense/Security, Immigration, Commerce, Infrastructure, Housing, Communications, Culture/Heritage, Audit/Oversight, Civil Registry; National Bank, Archives, Statistics, Electoral Commission, Supreme Court.

Elections & Civic Duty: citizen bills → signatures → House → President → Sabbath vote; mandatory participation penalties.

Emergency & Succession: Safe Reboot 3-of-5 elders, 180-min timelock, no fund transfers; Sabbath Safe Mode; Presidency returns to human via special election.

Sovereignty & Protection: digital-first; non-seizure; freedom of worship; high amendment thresholds.

Citizen Rewards & Lottery (buy-in): Buy-in only, 20% to Treasury, winners 40/25/15, eligibility requires voting + monthly job. (Constitutional text pending Article XI finalization.)




---

Architecture to Audit

On-chain (Sui/Move) modules:

citizenship.move — registry, sponsorship, World ID hooks, strikes.

escrow.move — job listing, acceptance, stablecoin escrow, release, tax withhold.

receipts.move — immutable event objects for jobs, votes, taxes, UBI, overrides.

treasury.move — tax intake, UBI schedule, circuit breakers, emergency pool, proof-of-reserves events.

governance.move — proposals, ballots, zk vote checks, penalties, override timelock.

(Planned) investment.move — auto-allocation, oracle-fed rebalancing, liquidity rules, emergency withdrawal protocol.

(Planned) lottery.move — buy-in tickets (NFT receipts), VRF/randomness, eligibility gates, payout splits (20% treasury; 40/25/15 winners).


Cross-chain / off-chain:

Oracles: prices (BTC/ETH/SUI/T-Bills), geo-compliance, randomness VRF; 3-of-5 independence.

Indexers: search/matching analytics; do not bloat on-chain state.

Compliance: dual-filing rails (tax/IP/grants), embargo/OFAC gating where required.

Storage: Arweave/IPFS for durable receipt snapshots.



---

Invariants & Properties (Please verify / refine)

1. Receipt immutability: No mutation or deletion; unique IDs; causal linkages (job→escrow→release→tax).


2. Escrow safety: No double-spend; no premature release; all paths end with either worker or refund, never both.


3. Tax correctness: Withholding applied deterministically at release; jurisdiction tag attached (oracle-fed).


4. UBI discipline: Never exceeds 70% of 90d inflows; runway ≥12 months or UBI auto-scales down.


5. Override limits: Only Presidency key can invoke; emits event; expires ≤30d unless ratified; cannot bypass treasury/UBI caps.


6. Voting uniqueness: One-human-one-vote via World ID proof; AIs/robots excluded from voting unless future law enables.


7. Reputation resistance: Stake-weighted + decay; low-value job spam excluded; wash trading slashes stake.


8. Investment guards: Allocation bands enforced; vol cap & liquidity floor enforced on-chain; rebalancing only with quorum oracles.


9. Lottery fairness: Buy-in only; eligibility gates; VRF randomness; deterministic payout splits; 20% to treasury.


10. Safe Reboot: 3-of-5, time-locked; cannot move funds; only restores validators / pauses risky modules.




---

Known Risks Raised (Address explicitly)

Legal recognition: We proceed as “digital-first nation platform/DAO”— code reflects compliance modules; statehood claims are symbolic.

Geo-compliance: Rely on oracle attestations + citizen-declared jurisdictions; enforce gating on payouts when required.

AI identity flood: AI-worker dual attestation (sponsor + unique AI key); per-sponsor quota & stake bonding; anomaly detection.

Reputation gaming: Min economic threshold per rating; decay; stake/bond slashing for collusion.

Treasury spiral: UBI circuit breakers + diversified revenue + sovereign investment engine with liquidity floor.

Override abuse: Hard on-chain timelock & citizen ratification; narrow scope; full receipts.

Cross-chain fragility: Graceful degradation if oracles fail; safe defaults (pause rebalancing, continue core ops).



